c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Orthopedic Fractures<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-350c227 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"350c227\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-aa401e2\" data-id=\"aa401e2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bf11904 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bf11904\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Gustilo Classification of Open Fractures<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Type I: Wound \u2264 1 cm &amp; Minimal Soft Tissue Damage\/Contamination<\/li><li>Type II: Wound 1-10 cm or Moderate Soft Tissue Damage<\/li><li>Type III:<ul><li>A: Wound &gt; 10 cm, Extensive Soft Tissue Damage or Contaminated<ul><li>Includes All Farm Injuries<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>B: Extensive Periosteal Stripping or Requiring Soft Tissue Coverage<\/li><li>C: Vascular Injury Requiring Repair<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Initial Management<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Evaluation:<ul><li>Always Evaluate <strong>Neurovascular<\/strong> Status First<\/li><li>If Fracture\/Dislocation with Weak\/No Pulse: Reduce and Reassess<ul><li>Still None: Surgical Vascular Repair<\/li><li>Weak: CTA<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Irrigation &amp; Debridement:<ul><li>Timing Within 24 Hours or As Soon As Possible if Contaminated<\/li><li>Use NS at Low Pressure, 3 L Per Successive Gustilo Type (I: 3L, II: 6L, III: 9L)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Antibiotics:<ul><li>Gustilo Type I\/II: First Generation Cephalosporin (Ancef)<\/li><li>Gustilo Type III: Add Gram Negative Coverage (Gentamicin)<\/li><li>Severe Contamination or Vascular Injury: Add Anaerobic Coverage (Penicillin)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Fracture Repair<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Early Operative Fixation Best<ul><li>High ISS: <strong>Delay<\/strong> 2-4 Days<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Bony Stabilization Before Vascular Reconstruction<\/strong><ul><li>If Extremity is Grossly Ischemic or Actively Hemorrhaging \u2013 Control with a Temporary Shunt &amp; Fasciotomy Prior to Bony Stabilization &amp; Then Vascular Reconstruction<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Options:<ul><li><em>Open Reduction and Internal Fixation (ORIF)<\/em><ul><li>Types: IM Nail vs. Plating<\/li><li>Generally Preferred<\/li><li><strong>Reduced Pulmonary<\/strong> Complications<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>External Fixation (Ex-Fix)<\/em><ul><li>Indications: Extensive Soft Tissue Destruction, Contamination or Associated Vascular Injury<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Throckmorton (John Thomas\/JT) Sign<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Definition: When the Male Penis Points in the Direction of Unilateral Injury<\/li><li>Classically Refers to Hip\/Pelvic Fractures Seen on Plain Film XR<\/li><li>Considered a Joke Term with No Real Diagnostic Utility<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-665772e\" data-id=\"665772e\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb0a32c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bb0a32c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11860 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/IM-Nail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"444\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/IM-Nail.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/IM-Nail-300x266.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>IM Nail <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5fbffe0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5fbffe0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11884 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Plating.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Plating.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Plating-300x194.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>ORIF Plating <sup>2<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c61f99a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c61f99a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11857 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/External-Fixation.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/External-Fixation.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/External-Fixation-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>External Fixation <sup>3<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fdb989 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4fdb989\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tex